params.markdown:
# IIS OpenTelemetry metrics

The dashboard provides a visual representation of IIS metrics collected via OpenTelemetry IIS receiver, it contains:

- Uptime, connection count, thread count
- Network traffic metrics
- Request count
- Request queue metrics

embeddableConfig.title: Total attempts to connect to the server
